pesticide.PPE: long-sleeved shirt and long pants, shoes plus socks

Active_Ingredients.name: Glyphosate, N-(phosphonomethyl)glycine, in the form of its isopropylamine salt

Safety_Information.general_Info: Keep out of reach of children. CAUTION! CAUSES MODERATE EYE IRRITATION. Avoid contact with eyes or clothing.
Safety_Information.if_In_Eyes: Hold eye open and rinse slowly and gently with water for 15-20 minutes. Remove contact lenses, if present, after the first 5 minutes, then continue rinsing eye. Call a poison control center or physician for treatment advice. Have the product container or label with you when calling a poison control center or physician, or going for treatment.
Safety_Information.physician_Note: Call a poison control center or physician for treatment advice.
